## Build Instructions

```bash
cd python

# Option 1: pip install
export GGML_PATH=/path/to/llama.cpp
pip install -e .

# Option 2: CMake
mkdir build && cd build
cmake -DGGML_PATH=/path/to/llama.cpp ..
make
```

