## Usage Example

```python
import nanobrain as nb

config = nb.UnifiedConfig()
kernel = nb.UnifiedKernel(config)
kernel.initialize()

atom_id = kernel.create_atom("ConceptNode", "Cat", 0.9, 0.8)
print(kernel.get_metrics())

kernel.shutdown()
```

